{"tid":1409553,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Be Water Be Humble 仇恨，係人之常情，但請保持理智","createTime":"2019-08-04T22:25:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T12:48:13.000Z","uid":247064,"like":51,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"06f2cd01a07bff7286efb0d32c7ce127ad02f8b5","tid":1409553,"uid":247064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:25:30.000Z","msg":"見到香港人咁樣俾黑警，港共，中共對待，嬲，係好正常，情緒，個個都有，我都唔會叫你地唔好嬲，唔好憎黑警。<br />\n<br />\n但，呢種情緒，仇恨應該係我地嘅動力，決心，而唔係被情緒支配，控制我地嘅行為。如果因為仇恨，控制唔到情緒就可以亂鳩咁發洩，咁我地同黑警有咩分別？就算我地推翻現今政權，都只不過係換咗另一批人上去，本質上同依家港洪，中共冇分別，我地要做嘅，係show俾其他人睇，我地比佢地更加好，更加適合去建立新香港。<br />\n<br />\nBe Water Be Humble Be a better man"},{"pid":"d6016bda6ad9944f4ae5216ed6a4cbf66a8a9fc7","tid":1409553,"uid":50457,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:27:55.000Z","msg":"不能讓仇恨滋生"},{"pid":"8fb7dba31cb12c8a576fbbb91b5a654cb4c13934","tid":1409553,"uid":247064,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"d6016bda6ad9944f4ae5216ed6a4cbf66a8a9fc7","tid":1409553,"uid":50457,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:27:55.000Z","msg":"不能讓仇恨滋生"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:30:10.000Z","msg":"係化仇恨為動力，不被仇恨控制"},{"pid":"505ed715e5012005d2d1bffed5cef649a1e9692d","tid":1409553,"uid":247064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:30:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a6263b0b20d561691fec764d0e8ef5b3bd664149","tid":1409553,"uid":247064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:33:12.000Z","msg":"Be Water! Be Humble! Be a better man!"},{"pid":"1dbc82f66fc98d616685d329c9e9fa3da95532f8","tid":1409553,"uid":247064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:37:13.000Z","msg":"Be Water! Be Humble! Be a better man!"},{"pid":"3519ef4bad9c74b33c1fc93aa12c2e719bbb7fa8","tid":1409553,"uid":296222,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:38:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1115e1b54116aa78352d46db1d5c1ec4